 “#VTA Supporting”等从 Virtual Talent Academy (VTA) X 官方账号中消失https://p2y.jp/virtual-talent-academy-vta-x-official-account-disappears-tag-supporting-vta-etc/ https://p2y.jp/virtual-talent-academy-vta-x-official-account-disappears-tag-supporting-vta-etc/#respondp2y_admin Thu, 05 Oct 2023 03:44:34 +0000 VTuberバーチャルANYCOLOR株式会社TwitterYouTuberにじさんじにじさんじプロジェクトバーチャルYouTuberバーチャル・タレント・アカデミー(VTA) https://p2y.jp/?p=102742 <p> 2023年10月4日，ANYCOLOR株式会社宣布旗下运营的VTuber培训项目“虚拟人才学院（VTA）”重聚。除此之外，同一个程序[...]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/virtual-talent-academy-vta-x-official-account-disappears-tag-supporting-vta-etc/">“#VTA 支持”的帖子从 Virtual Talent Academy (VTA) X 官方帐户中消失，首先</a>出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p> 2023年10月4日，ANYCOLOR株式会社宣布旗下运营的VTuber培训项目“<strong>虚拟人才学院</strong>（VTA）”重聚。与此同时，已确认“ <strong><em>#VTA Supporting</em></strong> ”等标签已从该项目的官方 X (Twitter) 帐户中删除。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"> <a href="https://x.com/VTA_ANYCOLOR?t=-rbs3MFWtXz7IEwoUZIfDw&amp;s=09" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img data-attachment-id="102746" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/virtual-talent-academy-vta-x-official-account-disappears-tag-supporting-vta-etc/virtual_talent_academy_vta_x_official_account_disappears_tag_supporting_vta_etc/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/virtual_talent_academy_vta_x_official_account_disappears_tag_supporting_vta_etc.png" data-orig-size="1200,676" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="virtual_talent_academy_vta_x_official_account_disappears_tag_supporting_vta_etc" data-image-description="" data-image-c