ro" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">K9KURO</a> ／<a href="https://www.vshojo.com/ja/talent/kuro" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">黑贝尼</a></p><cite>YouTube / X（推特）/ Twitch / VShojo</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>P2y.jp 经营代表“Mr.2（暂定）”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber 信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="vpL34CGsmb"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/vshojo-first-male-vtuber-kuro-kurenai-receives-worldwide-response-and-some-question-his-identity/">VShojo 首位男性 VTuber“Kuro Kurenai”获得全球回应，有人质疑他的身份</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VShojo 首位男性 VTuber“Kuro Kurenai”受到全球回应，有人质疑他的身份” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/vshojo-first-male-vtuber-kuro-kurenai-receives-worldwide-response-and-some-question-his-identity/embed/#?secret=oc5AU11IEM#?secret=vpL34CGsmb" data-secret="vpL34CGsmb" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vshojo-first-male-vtuber-kuro-kurenai-receives-worldwide-response-and-some-question-his-identity/">VShojo 后的第一位男性 VTuber“Kuro Kurenai”在国内外受到了广泛关注。寻找他“真实身份”的运动</a>首先出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/vshojo-first-male-vtuber-kuro-kurenai-receives-worldwide-response-and-some-question-his-identity/feed/ 0 102580
